📚 References

1) MDN: HTML (https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML)

2) MDN: HTML Elements Reference (https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element)

3) HTML Entities Character Chart (https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/named-characters.html#named-character-references)

4) MDN Web Glossary: Semantics (https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Glossary/Semantics)

5) w3Schools: Semantic HTML (https://www.w3schools.com/html/html5_semantic_elements.asp)

6) MDN: Document and Website Structure (https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML/Document_and_website_structure)



📚 HTML Table References:

1) MDN: Table Basics (https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Learn/HTML/Tables/Basics)

2) MDN: Advanced Tables and Accessibility (https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Learn/HTML/Tables/Advanced)



📚 HTML Forms References:

1) MDN: Web Forms (https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Learn/Forms)

2) MDN: Form Element (https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form)



